  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the high speed boat racing world of Jet Rush!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features real world physics with fluid simulated water but still has an arcade soul. Dive underwater and explore the undersea to find shortcuts! Race around the many locations in Jet Rush and get the best times! Unlock new cups and body styles as you fight for the best time!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Training Map</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A great place to start! Only takes 1 minute and teaches all the fundamentals! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>The Locations</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One second you're racing through the tropics enjoying that perfect sunset, the next you're deep in the swamps swatting away bugs. There's nothing like the mirror-like waters of a lake where there's no waves to challenge you, just your wits and the pedal to the metal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/dd8a87caa062faaf26230bbf39009edb.poster.avif?t=1766156823\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/dd8a87caa062faaf26230bbf39009edb.webm?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/dd8a87caa062faaf26230bbf39009edb.mp4?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>The Gallery</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock every boat and customize the paint jobs not just for you but for bragging rights!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/cc698082c96ef1e8ba35f1be1b142516.poster.avif?t=1766156823\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/cc698082c96ef1e8ba35f1be1b142516.webm?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/cc698082c96ef1e8ba35f1be1b142516.mp4?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Track Challenges</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for the Pyramid's, Mines, Spikes! Race as fast as you can to the finish line! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game is always evolving, stay tuned for more updates as we go!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/bd3152dd185ca519f45ee7e9b24dbde0.poster.avif?t=1766156823\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/bd3152dd185ca519f45ee7e9b24dbde0.webm?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/bd3152dd185ca519f45ee7e9b24dbde0.mp4?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the high speed boat racing world of Jet Rush!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features real world physics with fluid simulated water but still has an arcade soul. Dive underwater and explore the undersea to find shortcuts! Race around the many locations in Jet Rush and get the best times! Unlock new cups and body styles as you fight for the best time!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Training Map</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A great place to start! Only takes 1 minute and teaches all the fundamentals! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>The Locations</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One second you're racing through the tropics enjoying that perfect sunset, the next you're deep in the swamps swatting away bugs. There's nothing like the mirror-like waters of a lake where there's no waves to challenge you, just your wits and the pedal to the metal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/dd8a87caa062faaf26230bbf39009edb.poster.avif?t=1766156823\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/dd8a87caa062faaf26230bbf39009edb.webm?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/dd8a87caa062faaf26230bbf39009edb.mp4?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>The Gallery</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock every boat and customize the paint jobs not just for you but for bragging rights!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/cc698082c96ef1e8ba35f1be1b142516.poster.avif?t=1766156823\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/cc698082c96ef1e8ba35f1be1b142516.webm?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/cc698082c96ef1e8ba35f1be1b142516.mp4?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Track Challenges</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for the Pyramid's, Mines, Spikes! Race as fast as you can to the finish line! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game is always evolving, stay tuned for more updates as we go!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/bd3152dd185ca519f45ee7e9b24dbde0.poster.avif?t=1766156823\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/bd3152dd185ca519f45ee7e9b24dbde0.webm?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967680/extras/bd3152dd185ca519f45ee7e9b24dbde0.mp4?t=1766156823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
